tweet: Merry Christmas! Each year we have so many blessings to cherish, but on this day, we take time to celebrate the greatest gift of all, the birth of Jesus Christ. I hope your day is filled with peace, love, & joy. From my family to yours, Merry Christmas and blessings to you all.
